            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Contulinus">Gontulino</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Bonushomo">Bonomo</name></persName> e la moglie
                                <persName><name ref="Bona">Bona</name></persName> del <persName>fu
                                <name ref="Rodelandus">Rodilando</name></persName>, avendo ricevuto
                            <rs key="#Meritum/launechild">meritum argentum</rs> dai fratelli
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName> e
                            <persName key="#Other_clerics"><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">chierico</rs> del <persName>fu <name ref="Bonitius"
                                >Bonizio</name></persName>, promettono di non contestare medietatem
                        di un appezzamento di terra, quod est campo, posto in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/691">Pomaio</placeName> ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/691">Bocca Georgi</placeName>. Se non rispetteranno i
                        suddetti impegni, promettono con i loro eredi di versare ai fratelli e ai
                        loro eredi la pena di 3 libbre dâ€™argento. Chiedono al <rs
                            key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Hugo">Ugo</name></persName> la
                        stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>.
                                <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Rodelandus"
                                >Rodilando</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Homodeus"
                                >Omodei</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Bonushomo"
                                    >Bonomo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Cicco"
                            >Cigo</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
